| [<ffffffffa008bc95>] i915_get_vblank_timestamp+0x45/0xa0 [i915]
| CPU: 3 PID: 517 Comm: Xorg Not tainted 3.10.10-rt7+ #5
| Call Trace:
|  [<ffffffff8164b790>] dump_stack+0x19/0x1b
